Diamond::

She returned and saw the shuttle outside the base.  She walked in 
through the hangar bay door and went to find FZ. Using her 
commlink, "Commander FZ, I have finissshed my assssignment. I have 
the ssspecimensss that you have requesssted. What would you like me 
to do with them?"  She said, taking off the DNA collector.  She still 
didn't care why she went to get them. What she did care about was 
getting another chance to go and kill a pred leader or a maximal 
leader.
